White v. California.

Supreme Court of California. Motion for leave to file brief of National *876Lawyers Guild, as amicus curiae, denied. Certiorari denied.

William B. Esterman for petitioner. Edmund G. Brown, Attorney General of California, William V. O’Connor, Chief Deputy Attorney General, and Elizabeth Miller, Deputy Attorney General, for respondent.
